rows.label: tlk400905_msg0001
rows.name: So, what do you want to know?

rows.label: tlk400905_msg0002
rows.name:
If you have any information about certain
parts being bought in bulk or sold to
someone, Tora would like to know, mo.

rows.label: tlk400905_msg0003
rows.name: What kind of parts?

rows.label: tlk400905_msg0004
rows.name:
There are quite a few, mo... I'll
name them one by one, so if you
know anything, please tell me, mo.

rows.label: tlk400905_msg0005
rows.name: Eh? Are you doing that again?

rows.label: tlk400905_msg0006
rows.name: Tetra-Circle.

rows.label: tlk400905_msg0007
rows.name: Snake Joint.

rows.label: tlk400905_msg0008
rows.name: Black Ash.

rows.label: tlk400905_msg0009
rows.name: Wait! I've heard something about that.

rows.label: tlk400905_msg0010
rows.name: Momomo!? It's over already, mo?

rows.label: tlk400905_msg0011
rows.name: Masterpon looks disappointed, mo...

rows.label: tlk400905_msg0012
rows.name: Alright!

rows.label: tlk400905_msg0013
rows.name: Tell me more.

rows.label: tlk400905_msg0014
rows.name:
An old guy was saying he
regularly sells Black Ash.

rows.label: tlk400905_msg0015
rows.name:
It was a pretty big deal,
and he was bragging about
how he'd be set for a while.

rows.label: tlk400905_msg0016
rows.name:
Black Ash is a mineral used for
shielding ether furnaces, mo.

rows.label: tlk400905_msg0017
rows.name: This seems to be it.

rows.label: tlk400905_msg0018
rows.name:
Can you tell me where
to find that old guy?

rows.label: tlk400905_msg0019
rows.name: Hmmm...

rows.label: tlk400905_msg0020
rows.name: Huh? For some reason, I can't remember.

rows.label: tlk400905_msg0021
rows.name:
If you bought something, I
might be able to remember...

rows.label: tlk400905_msg0022
rows.name: This guy...
